text: Karichma Ekoh (born 4 March 1998) is a French female handball player who plays for ESBF Besançon. ==International honours== *Junior World Championship: **Gold Medalist: 2017 ==Individual awards== *Championnat de France Best Young Player: 2018 ==References== Category:French female handball players Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Clichy, Hauts-de-Seine
